Toyoka 28-Dec-17 05:25 AM
@NickIAm some particles require proper control point set up to function
if you open the particle in the particle editor, look at what control points it uses (on the right, there should be a space that shows the control point numbers, hover over them and they should tell you what particles use them and for what functions) (edited)
you can then set those control points on the info_particle_system
you can name the info_particle_system and allow the control points in the entity to target the entity itself by the name you gave it (edited)
if that makes sense
